<L>__{interior dubois mansion day}
<A>__{a globule of red liquid. a signet ring. marian seals a letter.}
<L>__{interior bishop's castle day}
<A>__{the letter is held in the pudgy, jeweled fingers of the bishop of hereford. a lavish office.}
<C>__{marian}
<D>__{it is a personal matter, my lord, but one of vital importance.}
<C>__{bishop}
<D>__{i understand, my dear lady. this is my most trusted emissary.}
<A>__{he hands the letter to a solemn courier.}
<C>__{marian}
<D>__{you will travel to france immediately. you must give this directly into the hands of the king, and him alone.}
<A>__{the courier bows in acknowledgement. marian indicates sarah.}
<C>__{marian}
<D>__{my lady in waiting will accompany you.}
<A>__{surprised, the courier glances at the bishop.}
<C>__{bishop}
<D>__{my dear, i could not vouch for her safety. the journey is fraught with danger.}
<C>__{marian}
<D>__{i appreciate your concern, my lord, but sarah is an accomplished rider. i must insist that she goes along.}
<C>__{bishop}
<P>__{(a beat)}
<D>__{as you wish.}
